## Scope of restriction

The following modules within this repository implement HSP:

- `quorum/hsp/gate.py` — fail-closed approval gate for evolution loops
- `quorum/hsp/ai_act_cert.py` — auto-certification for EU AI Act 2026-08
- `quorum/evolution/distillation.py` — model weight promotion (gated)
- `quorum/evolution/adversarial.py` — adversarial self-play (gated)
- `quorum/evolution/synthetic_data.py` — synthetic data generation (gated)

